<section class="cs-system">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--accent-gg);">System 03</p>
    <h3>Two views of every animation</h3>
    <p>First-person hands and a third-person body, both driven from the same animation set through Animation Layer Interfaces. Per-weapon ALIs swapped behavior cleanly. Aim offsets used Control Rotation rather than custom replicated variables, which removed a class of multiplayer bugs that had eaten weeks earlier in the project.</p>
    <span class="cs-tag">ALI</span><span class="cs-tag">Aim Offsets</span><span class="cs-tag">Control Rotation</span>
